The story of how Microsoft came to accept the reality of Windows=E2=80=99 d=
ecline is more interesting than the fact of Windows=E2=80=99 decline; this =
is how CEO Satya Nadella convinced the company to accept the obvious.

I then documented a few seminal decisions made to demote windows, including=
 releasing Office on iPad as soon as he took over, explicitly re-orienting =
Microsoft around services instead of devices ( https://stratechery.com/2013=
/services-not-devices/?access_token=3DeyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6InN0cmF0Z=
WNoZXJ5LnBhc3Nwb3J0Lm9ubGluZSIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJhdWQiOiJzdHJhdGVjaGVyeS5=
